                        text="&lt;p>Join us on a typical day in the life of an AbbVie employee driving change around the clock. We drop in on Sherri Carter, an associate director in our operations group. Sherri oversees a building and team that manufactures critical medicine. All while she does her part to promote greater diversity and inclusion by mentoring and nurturing talent.&lt;/p>"/>
